text: You Am I is a band from Sydney, Australia. It started in 1989 and plays alternative rock music. You Am I is famous for its lead singer Tim Rogers, for having lots of albums at number one on the ARIA Charts, and for their live music.Ed. Nimmervoll. You Am I > Overview. Allmusic. title: You Am I
